            "title": "南昌站匯璽 敞亮大廳原木色調 特闊窗賞海景",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"南昌站匯璽 敞亮大廳原木色調 特闊窗賞海景\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a7942983df29a5ed48c1c25bebc29918/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032113461647835.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">南昌站匯璽 敞亮大廳原木色調 特闊窗賞海景</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>南昌站上蓋臨海屋苑匯璽，享出行四通八達之優勢。今日介紹屋苑2A期海鑽匯中層A室，實用面積1,586方呎，3房2套連多用途房，廳大房大，內附豪華靚裝，可見海景，最新月租叫價85,000元，實用呎租約54元。\n\n</p>\n<p>據悉，今日參觀的單位業主已花費200萬元進行裝修，且斥資150萬元配置意大利進口家具。現場所見，空間甚為闊落，備有近落地玻璃，光猛通透，從玻璃外望見部分海景。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150478/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位為3房2套連多用途房設計，是家庭租客之選。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dcfefab8ca59c2d5aa79149f54cdbcb5/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_25_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位為3房2套連多用途房設計，是家庭租客之選。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150479/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"廚房附設多組儲物空間，輕鬆將廚具、煮食電器等分類。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e8e7f52c30537812735105c12eeae13c/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_25_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廚房附設多組儲物空間，輕鬆將廚具、煮食電器等分類。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150480/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"浴室設有窗戶，將濕氣排走。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3a36e2ca5509e1aa3c7922a793083fd/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_25_PM_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浴室設有窗戶，將濕氣排走。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150481/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"南昌站上蓋屋苑匯璽2A期海鑽匯中層A室，實用面積1586方呎，現時月租叫價85000元。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb54f5319dddd89ba793f353b4c8d11c/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_25_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        南昌站上蓋屋苑匯璽2A期海鑽匯中層A室，實用面積1586方呎，現時月租叫價85000元。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150483/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"匯璽外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fcb2e8882a7a6841ba68927588b4ea5a/2025-03/PL240805CW003_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        匯璽外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>1586呎3房2套間隔</h2>\n<p>放盤為3房2套設計，另有多用途房，所有房間皆方正實用，各個家庭成員有寬闊私人活動空間。\n\n</p>\n<p>單位有多個浴室，其中的浴室以雲石面鋪設，配搭浴缸等基本潔具，設窗戶排走濕氣。廚房方面，家電齊全，附設多組儲物櫃將各類物品收納。\n\n</p>\n<p>匯璽自設住客會所，提供包括室外泳池、健身室及燒烤場等設施，同時基座設有商場V Walk。\n\n</p><h2>必睇靚位</h2>\n<p>約200萬元豪裝，即租即住\n\n</p>\n<p>享海景，景致開揚\n\n</p>\n<p>多窗設計，空間光猛\n\n</p>\n<p>南昌站上蓋項目，交通方便\n\n</p><h2>放盤單位資料</h2>\n<p>物業名稱：匯璽\n\n</p>\n<p>地址 : 深旺道28號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：8年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：海鑽匯中層A室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：1586方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：3房2套連多用途房\n\n</p>\n<p>叫租：85000元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎租：54元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：美聯物業\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：9322 3339（黃小姐）\n\n</p>\n<p>*相片由代理提供\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
